k.', 267, 0), (409036, 'We never live  but we are always in the expectation of living.', 808, 0), (409037, 'Life  we learn too late  is in the living  in the tissue of every day and hour.', 9981, 0), (409038, 'There is time for work. And time for love. That leaves no other time.', 111, 0), (409039, 'It is not the years in your life but the life in your years that counts.', 28686, 0), (409040, 'A single event can awaken within us a stranger totally unknown to us. To live is to be slowly born.', 69, 0), (409041, 'One hour of life  crowded to the full with glorious action  and filled with noble risks  is worth whole years of those mean observances of paltry decorum.', 972, 0), (409042, 'The good life  as I conceive it  is a happy life. I do not mean that if you are good you will be happy - I mean that if you are happy you will be good.', 95, 0), (409043, 'One man in his time plays many parts.', 13, 0), (409044, 'He alone deserves liberty and life who daily must win them anew.', 62192, 0), (409045, 'One returns to the place one came from.', 2843, 0), (409046, 'The true meaning of life is to plant trees  under whose shade you do not expect to sit.', 64541, 0), (409047, 'It is now life and not art that requires the willing suspension of disbelief.', 13991, 0), (409048, 'The great use of life is to spend it for something that will outlast it.', 1782, 0), (409049, 'Life is painting a picture  not doing a sum.', 24754, 0), (409050, 'Go placidly amid the noise and the haste  and remember what peace there may be in silence. As far as possible without surrender  be on good terms with all persons. Speak your truth quietly and clearly  and listen to others  even the dull and ignorant  they too have their story. Be yourself. Especially do not feign affection. Neither be cynical about love - for in the face of all aridity and disenchantment it is as perennial as the grass. Take kindly the counsel of the years  gracefully surrendering the things of youth. Nurture strength of spirit 